ROME
Dong Kingman, the award winning Chinese-American artist, travels the world sketching and painting
the beautiful the monumental and the picturesque. His watercolors grace more than forty
permanent museum and private collections in the USA and abroad.
ROME. the Eternal City. is rich in artistic treasures. 2500 years of history lives on in the glorious
monuments, churches and ruins The Roman Forum, the Colosseum, the Vatican, St. Peters, the
Sistine Chapel, the Pantheon, the Spanish Steps, Trevi Fountain are just a few History is Rome's forte.
but the shops, food, wine, and the friendly people are renowned throughout the world. Pan Am
serves Rome every day directly from New York and Los Angeles.
